(514, 4, '2011-06-13 07:39:00', 'CJM Customer Group at Registration Extension Updated!', 'Our Customer Group at Registration extension, which gives the ability to set customer group at registration and checkout in various ways, has been updated to version 1.7.0. This version adds two new \"styles\", Drop-down with Allowed Groups and Guest List. Drop-down with Allowed Groups is just like Drop-down with All Groups, except you can exempt certain groups from showing up in the drop-down. Guest List is a cool feature where you can upload a CSV file of emails, and when a customer registers if their email address is in this list, they will be added to the group you specify. Contact me with your order number to get the updated files!', 'http://cjmstore.magenting.com/cjm-extensions/customer-group-at-registration.html', 1, 0),
(515, 4, '2011-06-06 09:00:00', 'CJM Swatch Extensions Updated!', 'Our image switching swatch extensions have been updated with requested features to show an image loader and work with image watermarks. Pre-Select Colors Plus Swatches is now at version 3.0.2 and Auto Swatches Plus is at version 2.6.6. Contact me with your order number to get the updated files.', 'http://cjmstore.magenting.com/cjm-extensions.html', 1, 0),
(516, 4, '2011-06-03 08:16:00', 'CJM Extensions now has notifications!', 'We now have notifications to keep you up to date on all our products!', 'http://www.chadjmorgan.com/', 1, 0),
